<p>The <code>html</code> module provides a typed layer over the raw <a href="/docs/reference/html/elem/" title="`html.elem`"><code>html.elem</code></a> function
that allows you to conveniently create HTML elements. HTML attributes are
exposed as function parameters that accept Typst types and automatically
take care of converting those into the appropriate HTML.</p>
